324
00:18:00.762 --> 00:18:02.347
[Prater]
Thank you. Charley.

325
00:18:05.934 --> 00:18:07.685
You're going to love Mia.

326
00:18:07.686 --> 00:18:10.522
[Dexter] <i>Time to see
