with nicknames is absurd.

361
00:19:37.859 --> 00:19:40.237
"Lady Vengeance"?

362
00:19:40.362 --> 00:19:44.115
If I were a guy.
I wouldn't be "Sir Vengeance."

363
00:19:48.078 --> 00:19:49.538
Grab a couple.

364
00:19:57.587 --> 00:19:59.548
[Dexter] <i>This is getting
better and better.</i>

365
00:20:02.384 --> 00:20:04.594
[gentle classical music playing]

366
00:20:05.971 --> 00:20:07.931
The man loves liberty. huh?

367
00:20:08.056 --> 00:20:09.431
Prater somehow got his hands on

368
00:20:09.432 --> 00:20:12.017
