409
00:21:49.240 --> 00:21:51.159
Al. meet Red.

410
00:21:51.284 --> 00:21:52.285
[Al]
Hey.

411
00:21:52.410 --> 00:21:54.329
Get in here. big guy.

412
00:21:55.121 --> 00:21:57.998
