- Oh. yeah.

415
00:22:01.378 --> 00:22:02.670
I got a whole litter of 'em.

416
00:22:02.671 --> 00:22:04.546
Actually. the last time
I saw you. I think

417
00:22:04.547 --> 00:22:06.173
