- [Dexter] <i>This guy</i>

421
00:22:12.806 --> 00:22:14.848
<i>has a thriving family?</i>

422
00:22:14.849 --> 00:22:16.517
<i>My son doesn't even
know I'm alive.</i>

423
00:22:16.518 --> 00:22:18.435
Aw. Babies that cute

424
00:22:18.436 --> 00:22:20.688
make me wish I had one.
But then I remember that

425
00:22:20.689 --> 00:22:22.107
- they shit their pants. so...
- Yeah.

426
00:22:22.232 --> 00:22:23.524
They do shit a lot. yeah.

427
00:22:23.525 --> 00:22:25.609
So. how do you
have space for both

428
00:22:25.610 --> 00:22:26.902
