so I can better

434
00:22:34.577 --> 00:22:36.079
show up for my family.

435
00:22:36.204 --> 00:22:38.957
It's not selfish.
It's self-care.

436
00:22:39.082 --> 00:22:41.208
[Dexter]
<i>Like the flight attendant says.</i>

437
00:22:41.209 --> 00:22:42.752
<i>affix your own mask first.</i>

438
00:22:42.877 --> 00:22:45.922
Plus. my wife enjoys
the hefty Prater bonus.

439
00:22:46.047 --> 00:22:48.215
But the best thing
is the time I get to spend

440
00:22:48.216 --> 00:22:50.427
with this group.
You know. it's not-it's not

441
