450
00:23:07.819 --> 00:23:08.987
Me neither.

451
00:23:09.112 --> 00:23:10.488
[elevator bell dings]

452
00:23:10.613 --> 00:23:15.243
What up. Rapunzel.
you big tub of shit?

453
00:23:15.368 --> 00:23:16.368
