or do you sharpen them yourself?

480
00:24:12.342 --> 00:24:13.550
[Al] No. no. I got a stone.

481
00:24:13.551 --> 00:24:15.136
I've got a disc.
I've got a belt grinder

482
00:24:15.261 --> 00:24:16.887
