489
00:24:26.981 --> 00:24:29.567
Hey. buddy.
catch us up on your year.

490
00:24:29.692 --> 00:24:31.110
I'd rather not.

491
00:24:31.236 --> 00:24:34.739
Oh. Gare-bear. my guy. try not
